{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":833,"text":"We are all activists now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":3600,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":4920,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":6680,"text":"I'll just stop here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":8039,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9240,"text":"From the families who are fighting\nto maintain funding for public schools,"},{"time":14640,"text":"the tens of thousands of people\nwho joined Occupy Wall Street"},{"time":19040,"text":"or marched with Black Lives Matter"},{"time":21240,"text":"to protest police brutality\nagainst African Americans,"},{"time":25760,"text":"families that join rallies,"},{"time":28280,"text":"pro-life and pro-choice,"},{"time":31600,"text":"those of us who are afraid"},{"time":33360,"text":"that our friends and neighbors\nare going to be deported"},{"time":36760,"text":"or that they'll be added to lists"},{"time":38760,"text":"because they are Muslim,"},{"time":41480,"text":"people who advocate for gun rights\nand for gun control"},{"time":46640,"text":"and the millions of people\nwho joined the women's marches"},{"time":50160,"text":"all across the country this last January."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52960,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":55640,"text":"We are all activists now,"},{"time":57760,"text":"and that means that we all have something\nto worry about from surveillance."},{"time":63320,"text":"Surveillance means\ngovernment collection and use"},{"time":66040,"text":"of private and sensitive data about us."},{"time":69280,"text":"And surveillance is essential"},{"time":71240,"text":"to law enforcement\nand to national security."},{"time":74360,"text":"But the history of surveillance"},{"time":76360,"text":"is one that includes surveillance abuses"},{"time":79880,"text":"where this sensitive information\nhas been used against people"},{"time":83360,"text":"because of their race,"},{"time":84920,"text":"their national origin,"},{"time":86720,"text":"their sexual orientation,"},{"time":88800,"text":"and in particular,\nbecause of their activism,"},{"time":92000,"text":"their political beliefs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94760,"text":"About 53 years ago,"},{"time":97400,"text":"Dr. Martin Luther King Jr.\ngave his \"I have a dream\" speech"},{"time":100960,"text":"on the Mall in Washington."},{"time":103040,"text":"And today the ideas behind this speech\nof racial equality and tolerance"},{"time":107760,"text":"are so noncontroversial"},{"time":109720,"text":"that my daughters\nstudy the speech in third grade."},{"time":113160,"text":"But at the time,"},{"time":114520,"text":"Dr. King was extremely controversial."},{"time":117520,"text":"The legendary and notorious\nFBI Director J. Edgar Hoover believed,"},{"time":123040,"text":"or wanted to believe,"},{"time":124880,"text":"that the Civil Rights Movement\nwas a Soviet communist plot"},{"time":128479,"text":"intended to destabilize\nthe American government."},{"time":132080,"text":"And so Hoover had his agents\nput bugs in Dr. King's hotel rooms,"},{"time":138360,"text":"and those bugs picked up conversations\nbetween civil rights leaders"},{"time":143920,"text":"talking about the strategies and tactics\nof the Civil Rights Movement."},{"time":149080,"text":"They also picked up sounds of Dr. King"},{"time":151320,"text":"having sex with women\nwho were not his wife,"},{"time":154200,"text":"and J. Edgar Hoover\nsaw the opportunity here"},{"time":156960,"text":"to discredit and undermine\nthe Civil Rights Movement."},{"time":161400,"text":"The FBI sent a package of these recordings"},{"time":165040,"text":"along with a handwritten note to Dr. King,"},{"time":168880,"text":"and a draft of this note\nwas found in FBI archives years later,"},{"time":175280,"text":"and the letter said,"},{"time":177040,"text":"\"You are no clergyman and you know it."},{"time":179840,"text":"King, like all frauds,\nyour end is approaching.\""},{"time":184040,"text":"The letter even seemed\nto encourage Dr. King to commit suicide,"},{"time":189560,"text":"saying, \"King, there is\nonly one thing left for you to do."},{"time":193360,"text":"You know what it is."},{"time":194960,"text":"You better take it before\nyour filthy, abnormal, fraudulent self"},{"time":199320,"text":"is bared to the nation.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":201200,"text":"But the important thing is,"},{"time":202640,"text":"Dr. King was not abnormal."},{"time":204880,"text":"Every one of us has something\nthat we want to hide from somebody."},{"time":210000,"text":"And even more important,"},{"time":211840,"text":"J. Edgar Hoover wasn't abnormal either."},{"time":215080,"text":"The history of surveillance abuses"},{"time":217040,"text":"is not the history\nof one bad, megalomaniacal man."},{"time":221080,"text":"Throughout his decades at the FBI,"},{"time":224120,"text":"J. Edgar Hoover enjoyed the support\nof the presidents that he served,"},{"time":227880,"text":"Democratic and Republican alike."},{"time":230680,"text":"After all, it was John F. Kennedy\nand his brother Robert Kennedy"},{"time":234040,"text":"who knew about and approved\nthe surveillance of Dr. King."},{"time":238640,"text":"Hoover ran a program\ncalled COINTELPRO for 15 years"},{"time":243080,"text":"which was designed\nto spy on and undermine civic groups"},{"time":247880,"text":"that were devoted\nto things like civil rights,"},{"time":250640,"text":"the Women's Rights Movement,"},{"time":252400,"text":"and peace groups and anti-war movements."},{"time":255160,"text":"And the surveillance didn't stop there."},{"time":257959,"text":"Lyndon Baines Johnson,"},{"time":259680,"text":"during the election campaign,"},{"time":261720,"text":"had the campaign airplane\nof his rival Barry Goldwater bugged"},{"time":267720,"text":"as part of his effort\nto win that election."},{"time":271200,"text":"And then, of course, there was Watergate."},{"time":275520,"text":"Burglars were caught"},{"time":277000,"text":"breaking into the Democratic\nNational Committee headquarters"},{"time":279880,"text":"at the Watergate Hotel,"},{"time":281440,"text":"the Nixon administration was involved\nin covering up the burglary,"},{"time":285640,"text":"and eventually Nixon\nhad to step down as president."},{"time":290040,"text":"COINTELPRO and Watergate\nwere a wake-up call for Americans."},{"time":294800,"text":"Surveillance was out of control"},{"time":296680,"text":"and it was being used\nto squelch political challengers."},{"time":301240,"text":"And so Americans rose to the occasion"},{"time":303800,"text":"and what we did was\nwe reformed surveillance law."},{"time":308160,"text":"And the primary tool we used\nto reform surveillance law"},{"time":312560,"text":"was to require a search warrant"},{"time":315280,"text":"for the government to be able to get\naccess to our phone calls and our letters."},{"time":321720,"text":"Now, the reason why\na search warrant is important"},{"time":324600,"text":"is because it interposes a judge"},{"time":326960,"text":"in the relationship\nbetween investigators and the citizens,"},{"time":330600,"text":"and that judge's job is to make sure"},{"time":333600,"text":"that there's good cause\nfor the surveillance,"},{"time":336240,"text":"that the surveillance\nis targeted at the right people,"},{"time":339680,"text":"and that the information that's collected"},{"time":342200,"text":"is going to be used\nfor legitimate government purposes"},{"time":345840,"text":"and not for discriminatory ones."},{"time":348800,"text":"This was our system,"},{"time":350040,"text":"and what this means is"},{"time":351320,"text":"that President Obama\ndid not wiretap Trump Tower."},{"time":355160,"text":"The system is set up to prevent\nsomething like that from happening"},{"time":360000,"text":"without a judge being involved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362480,"text":"But what happens when we're not talking\nabout phone calls or letters anymore?"},{"time":368520,"text":"Today, we have technology"},{"time":371240,"text":"that makes it cheap and easy\nfor the government to collect information"},{"time":375440,"text":"on ordinary everyday people."},{"time":378560,"text":"Your phone call records"},{"time":381280,"text":"can reveal whether you have an addiction,"},{"time":384920,"text":"what your religion is,"},{"time":386400,"text":"what charities you donate to,"},{"time":389080,"text":"what political candidate you support."},{"time":392040,"text":"And yet, our government\ncollected, dragnet-style,"},{"time":396160,"text":"Americans' calling records for years."},{"time":400320,"text":"In 2012, the Republican\nNational Convention"},{"time":404480,"text":"highlighted a new technology\nit was planning to use,"},{"time":407880,"text":"facial recognition,"},{"time":409400,"text":"to identify people\nwho were going to be in the crowd"},{"time":412400,"text":"who might be activists or troublemakers"},{"time":414880,"text":"and to stop them ahead of time."},{"time":417200,"text":"Today, over 50 percent of American adults"},{"time":420920,"text":"have their faceprint\nin a government database."},{"time":423920,"text":"The Bureau of Alcohol,\nTobacco, Firearms and Explosives"},{"time":427240,"text":"concocted a plan"},{"time":428800,"text":"to find out what Americans\nwere going to gun shows"},{"time":432360,"text":"by using license plate detectors"},{"time":434880,"text":"to scan the license plates of cars"},{"time":437000,"text":"that were in the parking lots\nof these events."},{"time":439880,"text":"Today, we believe that over 70 percent\nof police departments"},{"time":444320,"text":"have automatic license plate\ndetection technology"},{"time":447440,"text":"that they're using to track people's cars\nas they drive through town."},{"time":451960,"text":"And all of this information,"},{"time":454600,"text":"the license plates, the faceprints,"},{"time":457560,"text":"the phone records,"},{"time":459160,"text":"your address books, your buddy lists,"},{"time":462000,"text":"the photos that you upload\nto Dropbox or Google Photos,"},{"time":466440,"text":"and sometimes even\nyour chats and your emails"},{"time":470440,"text":"are not protected\nby a warrant requirement."},{"time":473760,"text":"So what that means is we have\nall of this information on regular people"},{"time":479360,"text":"that's newly available\nat very low expense."},{"time":483040,"text":"It is the golden age for surveillance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486480,"text":"Now, every parent is going\nto understand what this means."},{"time":491800,"text":"When you have a little baby"},{"time":493960,"text":"and the baby's young,"},{"time":495920,"text":"that child is not able\nto climb out of its crib."},{"time":499200,"text":"But eventually your little girl gets older"},{"time":502120,"text":"and she's able to climb out of the crib,"},{"time":505080,"text":"but you tell her,\n\"Don't climb out of the crib. OK?\""},{"time":508880,"text":"And every parent knows\nwhat's going to happen."},{"time":511080,"text":"Some of those babies\nare going to climb out of the crib."},{"time":514559,"text":"Right? That's the difference\nbetween ability and permission."},{"time":518240,"text":"Well, the same thing is true\nwith the government today."},{"time":520880,"text":"It used to be that our government\ndidn't have the ability"},{"time":523679,"text":"to do widespread, massive surveillance\non hundreds of millions of Americans"},{"time":527280,"text":"and then abuse that information."},{"time":529520,"text":"But now our government has grown up,"},{"time":531400,"text":"and we have that technology today."},{"time":534200,"text":"The government has the ability,"},{"time":536800,"text":"and that means the law\nis more important than ever before."},{"time":540400,"text":"The law is supposed to say"},{"time":542160,"text":"when the government\nhas permission to do it,"},{"time":546200,"text":"and it's supposed to ensure\nthat there's some kind of ramification."},{"time":550360,"text":"We notice when those laws are broken"},{"time":552880,"text":"and there's some of kind of\nramification or punishment."},{"time":555600,"text":"The law is more important than ever\nbecause we are now living in a world"},{"time":559040,"text":"where only rules\nare stopping the government"},{"time":561160,"text":"from abusing this information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563120,"text":"But the law has fallen down on the job."},{"time":565840,"text":"Particularly since September 11\nthe law has fallen down on the job,"},{"time":569800,"text":"and we do not have\nthe rules in place that we need."},{"time":573400,"text":"And we are seeing\nthe ramifications of that."},{"time":576200,"text":"So fusion centers\nare these joint task forces"},{"time":579480,"text":"between local, state\nand federal government"},{"time":581800,"text":"that are meant to ferret out\ndomestic terrorism."},{"time":585040,"text":"And what we've seen\nis fusion center reports"},{"time":587560,"text":"that say that you might be dangerous"},{"time":591360,"text":"if you voted for a third-party candidate,"},{"time":594320,"text":"or you own a \"Don't Tread On Me\" flag,"},{"time":597520,"text":"or you watched movies that are anti-tax."},{"time":601880,"text":"These same fusion centers have spied\non Muslim community groups' reading lists"},{"time":606680,"text":"and on Quakers who are resisting\nmilitary recruiting in high schools."},{"time":612680,"text":"The Internal Revenue Service\nhas disproportionately audited"},{"time":616880,"text":"groups that have \"Tea Party\"\nor \"Patriot\" in their name."},{"time":620560,"text":"And now customs and border patrol"},{"time":623160,"text":"is stopping people\nas they come into the country"},{"time":625960,"text":"and demanding our social\nnetworking passwords"},{"time":629160,"text":"which will allow them\nto see who our friends are,"},{"time":631760,"text":"what we say"},{"time":633000,"text":"and even to impersonate us online."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636520,"text":"Now, civil libertarians like myself"},{"time":639200,"text":"have been trying to draw\npeople's attention to these things"},{"time":643360,"text":"and fighting against them for years."},{"time":645960,"text":"This was a huge problem\nduring the Obama administration,"},{"time":650960,"text":"but now the problem is worse."},{"time":654520,"text":"When the New York Police Department"},{"time":657000,"text":"spies on Muslims"},{"time":658720,"text":"or a police department\nuses license plate detectors"},{"time":662600,"text":"to find out where\nthe officers' spouses are"},{"time":666520,"text":"or those sorts of things,"},{"time":667800,"text":"that is extremely dangerous."},{"time":669920,"text":"But when a president repurposes the power"},{"time":673000,"text":"of federal surveillance\nand the federal government"},{"time":675520,"text":"to retaliate against political opposition,"},{"time":678600,"text":"that is a tyranny."},{"time":680480,"text":"And so we are all activists now,"},{"time":684640,"text":"and we all have something\nto fear from surveillance."},{"time":688760,"text":"But just like in the time\nof Dr. Martin Luther King,"},{"time":692560,"text":"we can reform the way things are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695920,"text":"First of all, use encryption."},{"time":699120,"text":"Encryption protects your information"},{"time":702040,"text":"from being inexpensively\nand opportunistically collected."},{"time":706880,"text":"It rolls back the golden age\nfor surveillance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712080,"text":"Second, support surveillance reform."},{"time":715720,"text":"Did you know that if you have a friend"},{"time":717920,"text":"who works for the French\nor German governments"},{"time":721040,"text":"or for an international human rights group"},{"time":724200,"text":"or for a global oil company"},{"time":727600,"text":"that your friend is a valid\nforeign intelligence target?"},{"time":731920,"text":"And what that means is that when\nyou have conversations with that friend,"},{"time":736080,"text":"the US government\nmay be collecting that information."},{"time":740320,"text":"And when that information is collected,"},{"time":743600,"text":"even though it's\nconversations with Americans,"},{"time":745800,"text":"it can then be funneled to the FBI"},{"time":748920,"text":"where the FBI is allowed\nto search through it"},{"time":751400,"text":"without getting a warrant,"},{"time":752800,"text":"without probable cause,"},{"time":754480,"text":"looking for information about Americans"},{"time":756720,"text":"and whatever crimes we may have committed"},{"time":760160,"text":"with no need to document\nany kind of suspicion."},{"time":763920,"text":"The law that allows some of this to happen"},{"time":766920,"text":"is called Section 702\nof the FISA Amendments Act,"},{"time":771040,"text":"and we have a great opportunity this year,"},{"time":773600,"text":"because Section 702\nis going to expire at the end of 2017,"},{"time":778360,"text":"which means that\nCongress's inertia is on our side"},{"time":783000,"text":"if we want reform."},{"time":784600,"text":"And we can pressure our representatives"},{"time":788320,"text":"to actually implement\nimportant reforms to this law"},{"time":791840,"text":"and protect our data\nfrom this redirection and misuse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":796560,"text":"And finally, one of the reasons\nwhy things have gotten so out of control"},{"time":801600,"text":"is because so much\nof what happens with surveillance --"},{"time":804520,"text":"the technology, the enabling rules\nand the policies"},{"time":809080,"text":"that are either there\nor not there to protect us --"},{"time":812680,"text":"are secret or classified."},{"time":815120,"text":"We need transparency,\nand we need to know as Americans"},{"time":819360,"text":"what the government is doing in our name"},{"time":821920,"text":"so that the surveillance that takes place\nand the use of that information"},{"time":826520,"text":"is democratically accounted for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":830400,"text":"We are all activists now,"},{"time":832520,"text":"which means that we all have something\nto worry about from surveillance."},{"time":836720,"text":"But like in the time\nof Dr. Martin Luther King,"},{"time":840160,"text":"there is stuff that we can do about it."},{"time":842480,"text":"So please join me, and let's get to work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":847000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848240,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}